      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine showroom condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to every mechanical and aesthetic detail. The exterior finish retains its original luster, while the interior environment remains entirely undisturbed, reflecting a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is an acquisition for the discerning client who demands excellence and accepts no compromise in quality or performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
